{"tid":1266681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係社工都係香港人","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T04:13:26.000Z","uid":198310,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a32e4a624e07516e412ffccfdf88b432de1f573a","tid":1266681,"uid":198310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"可能因為啱啱個Post個名改得唔好，所以無咩人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係一個小薯社工，見到今晚嘅新聞真係好心痛。<br />\n我知好多人都會覺得無力同憤怒，好多負面情緒。甚至可能選擇離開我地咁多位戰友。<br />\n呢條抗爭之路我都唔知要行幾耐，但係香港咁壓迫嘅環境我地都生存到，有咩可以難到我地香港人。<br />\n我有一個心願就係一齊出黎嘅戰友，每一個都可以平平安安返屋企。<br />\n我真係唔想再見到有任何一位戰友離開。見到熱門愈黎愈多負面Post真係好擔心。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家好想搵人傾下可以選擇係連登開post,可以選擇搵朋友傾。<br />\n如果大家搵唔到人傾，可以tg我。絕對保密。或者想搵人吹下水都可以TG我。只係希望用我嘅能力做少少野。<br />\n香港人我地贏要一齊贏！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkpplsupport\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpplsupport&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=44b09c01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/hkpplsupport</a>"},{"pid":"0e8719c2f4e0dcf62a83bca2837dc111c477222c","tid":1266681,"uid":220144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6badbfbc77527a036ddf05ab729c687fe06cd1e","tid":1266681,"uid":198310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:12:28.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"24a6c1178c62207df3d6af495f2fd00216622b62","tid":1266681,"uid":6245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b83af88afe654cc9740af5d97d76830fcc9d50","tid":1266681,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0198610e1c7c8799672bcde9bda9e3eb627a685d","tid":1266681,"uid":25062